# React
* Functional components only.  Exported components ≤ 250 LOC.
* Explicit `Props` interface/type for every component.

# State
* One **Zustand** store per feature in `app/frontend/src/features/<name>/<name>Store.ts`.
* Provide `getInitialState()` for tests; persist with `zustand/middleware`.

# Styling & UI
* Tailwind CSS only; no inline `style` or separate `.css` files.
* Use **shadcn/ui** primitives; compose classes with `tailwind-merge`.
* Enforce Tailwind class order: layout → box → typography → colour → effect.

# Routing & Data
* Route comps reside in `app/frontend/src/pages/`; lazy-load with `React.lazy` + `Suspense`.
* Only route comps fetch data; children are presentational.

# A11y & Performance
* Must pass **eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y**.

* Virtualise lists > 100 items with `@tanstack/react-virtual`.